  "content": "ses the term abilities to refer to Skills of a character or some other active or passive function they possess.\n\nAbility Score & Ability Modifier\n\nIt's the number that represents each ability stat of your character. On the other hand, ability modifier is the bonus or penalty you gain from your ability score of each ability. To determine an ability modifier, subtract 10 to the ability score, then divide the result by two rounded down. For example. if you have 20 Strength, your ability score is 21",
